  <text>
     <body>
     <div xml:lang="lat" type="poem">
   <lg>
      <pb facs="2"/>
      <l>QVód CRVCE cuncta tuâ purgas mea crimina CHRISTE,</l>
      <l>Tu Redamandus eris Redimens; Redimar Redamando:</l>
      <l>Vt sic non Redamem nisi quae REDAMANDA Redemptus.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>Hinc mihi tuta Quies, et Honos; PVLVINAR honores</l>
      <l>Signat; BIS-BINVM format CRVX ALBA{que} firmat;</l>
      <l>Te, sancté, et dignè, et synceré vt semper Honorem.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>AREA sanguinea est, Fugiam quó ad Sanguinis Aram</l>
      <l>CHRISTE tui, et curas inter securè quiescam.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>CRVX dignum, tutum PVLVIN, facit ARRA firmum;</l>
      <l>Indè REDEMPTOREM vt Redamem; &amp; REDAMANDA Re<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>demptus</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <signed>A. N.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
